        <p class="section-eyebrow">Related</p>
        <h2 class="section-headline">More from the gear bag.</h2>
        <div class="related-grid">
          <a href="/learn/clean-football-pads/" class="related-card">
            <h3>How to clean football pads</h3>
            <p>The other major-pad sport. Same chemistry, more pieces.</p>
